                  <interp inst="t18270712-160-crimeloc884" type="placeName" value="Air-street-hill"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18270712-160-crimeloc884" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-160-off882 t18270712-160-crimeloc884"></join>. On the 20th of June, about six o'clock in the morning, I saw this property safe in the shop; I had seen the prisoner and two others about the house - he then had a blue coat on; I heard a cry of Stop thief! ran, and missed the knives and forks from my window; Hancock secured the prisoner, and Brown picked them up, as the prisoner threw them down.</p>
               <p>
            
