                     <interp inst="t18270712-160-person863" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner and two others loitering about for some hours; I then saw the prisoner take the knives - I ran out of my father's shop, which is just by, and called Stop thief! he threw them down - I took them up, and saw him taken; I did not lose sight of him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never had a blue coat on; I did not take them, and was not in company with any body.</p>
